  "labels": [
    "점보 팁"
  ],
  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8c81b70e-2043-4c04-a0ca-fbb5f8a1f241\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-52af949a-b490-4a70-95fd-3b614cb1d720\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-437698d9-08a2-4cc1-aaad-5468d80c6ebb\" style=\"color:#000000;\">🌸</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-211c6cb0-eb1a-43d4-9411-e823f64b028b\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-cfd8ca8f-2008-4958-9209-ed9c2d92a0c3\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-47d1c73e-7c26-4d12-951a-0062c6bac7c3\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-02fb2623-67e5-4951-bf14-8841fcab10ae\" style=\"color:#000000;\">따뜻한 봄날, 벚꽃 풍경을 담은 사진은 누구에게나 소중한 기억입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0eece6f5-2827-42d0-afd6-2661810ca534\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-fd661164-61ac-4781-8832-6acf2e2fd0d8\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>스마트폰으로 찍은 사진을 미니포토프린터로 바로 뽑는 것도 편리하지만, 벚꽃처럼 색감이 섬세한 사진은 품질이 중요한데, 미니포토프린터는 출력 품질이 아쉽다는 평가도 많습니다. </b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6a215067-3cb0-45bd-892b-21711efc1dd2\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7af5a477-0b5a-443b-b455-c6083042486c\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><u>벚꽃 사진의 분위기와 색을 제대로 담으려면 더 정교하고 선명한 방식이 필요합니다.</u></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-e27ab34f-0369-47ab-8627-2aa367166827\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-fad26593-5eca-4bea-8eb8-cff238c88839\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f04da35d-a39f-46ab-aa13-75a4b67ef1df\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-default\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-08600180-4392-4d25-b5cd-1711b03db226\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-4735b167-f6c2-42bd-9d64-d3c46ad33d94\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>그래서 요즘 많은 분이 포토북을 선택합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3d221de1-55b8-46a9-bbc2-e505792b589b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-17fa34dc-e771-4c23-a03d-20a03eeeefe1\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-e2418d44-8ca1-4d17-b158-edf45bfa5210\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b08e3581-2310-4cd4-a8f8-639cf2142508\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223833173933/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-754b0a86-e2b0-4909-b786-7d74674e09f8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-df1a85b7-aafe-4a9b-8c05-0b787ec0fbb3\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-8b240efb-1299-4b6f-a921-1d5f335317fe\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-2541e2fe-01cc-4e60-8824-2668fdae3de2\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-2237b0cf-1fe3-4a8e-a647-44f00684b649\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">이</span>번 글에서는 벚꽃 사진을 포토북으로 남기면 좋은 이유와 포토북을 만들 때 꼭 살펴봐야 할 기준을 알려드리겠습니다. 사진을 그냥 모아두는 것이 아니라, 보기 좋게 정리해 오래 간직하려면 포토북이 어떤 점에서 유리한지 끝까지 읽고 확인해 보시길 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-ead6336b-1b8b-4d59-964e-b19cc9a15b0d\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-e0e67a07-93de-42b3-a080-8f6e05a82f6f\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-02b96bda-02a2-48f0-8fd1-9ee69d60f637\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-146ccdc1-6d2a-420b-972e-2ea9e38296b9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-67f3b936-4979-4c5d-95cc-c30364d53b4d\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>\"미니포토프린터? 포토북이 좋은 이유\"</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-83a09963-dcd5-4f20-b92a-5a85ecc4cd7a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223833173933/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4ccff535-6d5a-4f5b-ad05-d79adb6e3a04\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-c8a212f3-b8a0-4617-9459-dc546e25dcb0\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-886fb5b6-91e0-4e8f-b07e-c72c52261080\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-b37807a0-21c1-42db-aa7c-fb1d93258622\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-d9ea5518-39bd-47a3-b159-129e27ba6e07\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">포</span>토북은 사진 정리에 실용적인 방법입니다. </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-d79e75d1-7d6a-45a7-8f15-5a8a36d07961\" style=\"color:#000000;\">스마트폰에 저장된 사진은 시간이 지나면 묻히기 쉽고, 다시 꺼내보기 어려울 수 있기 때문입니다.</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-3d799e35-c5d5-4d67-a587-c56ac2126280\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><u> 물론 미니포토프린터로 뽑은 사진은 귀엽고 간단하지만, 보관이나 감상 측면에서는 아쉬움이 많습니다. </u></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-9d0d514b-f60b-4088-9f2d-13dba5efdb94\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><u><b>​</b></u></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-06221ce1-fea3-4a16-8365-6024c0d7877f\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>하지만 포토북은 책처럼 넘기며 볼 수 있어서 훨씬 실용적이고 보기 좋습니다. </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-ec09471d-76d6-4c7e-9e1e-759ccfe94d6d\" style=\"color:#000000;\">특히 벚꽃처럼 계절을 담은 사진은 포토북으로 남기면 그 계절의 느낌까지 오래 간직할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-c7fc9aa6-e702-4df7-901e-bc8217251fed\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-5bbcb9fa-bac8-496f-987b-539200c79dbb\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d574db4d-1b72-4ffc-88dd-8f90e8507a67\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223833173933/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-805db3e3-492c-426c-8b28-b1f0c6b2976c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-0e0d67d3-6e4b-446a-a27f-188d6414c463\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-db4686a1-3aa8-4e9f-9131-5fcf40827162\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-7705029f-4819-46a4-8c24-664e9982a1f8\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-78d5829f-536d-4ed3-a55d-764a81e43725\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">게</span>다가 사진을 스토리처럼 구성할 수 있어서, 단순히 보관하는 것이 아니라 추억을 정리하는 방식으로 좋습니다.</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-27193067-a3e5-4fc6-8b1d-3d871a737cb4\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> 미니포토프린터로 만든 사진은 따로 정리하거나 보관하는 게 번거롭지만, 포토북은 한 번에 깔끔하게 정리할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-73bd9caf-d9b3-4ec1-921f-9bf8e6b11867\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-c01f246e-5cac-455a-820c-9a7b8439aa49\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-c7d5665a-b179-4c38-b663-508f22e63c9b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f2dafa65-64ba-4400-b6db-709c5ee0c852\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-f3c9b641-83eb-4ada-9567-1896e2376d8f\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>\"포토북을 만들 때 어떤 점을 확인해야 할까요?\"</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b8e75667-b2e1-40cb-bbcc-0840e2713e57\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223833173933/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-99a0ffc4-9067-4606-8062-84f298fc2166\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-241e6c0d-be1c-450d-af10-349ac86595fb\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-3b5505d3-d0c9-4b0d-873f-cdd59eb5393d\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-77489f87-fcb7-4987-9c26-3b306d12d239\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-9abf7cb0-bd30-4d2d-a8f5-f964b402f10c\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">먼</span>저 살펴볼 건 인쇄 품질과 종이입니다. </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-083ca71b-8a6f-40ea-b6df-d36eca8e3d5e\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><u>포토북은 오랫동안 보관해야 하니까 색이 바래거나 종이가 상하면 안 됩니다. </u></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-afdd219b-1447-4f5c-838b-2570485968db\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b>점보포토 포토북은 고급 인디고 인쇄 방식을 사용해 색이 정확하고 선명하게 표현됩니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-95f9d8d1-058c-4d93-ba05-cacf1a949236\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-071cf54e-74f3-40e9-b892-035065ba9028\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-25a6e3b8-b28e-4917-bd9f-728e6442aec1\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-8dfd4bb0-f12a-4d94-b8ff-29f9f3663f03\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b>종이도 랑데뷰 160g 고급지를 써서 튼튼하고 고급스럽습니다. </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-f3bd5c26-5471-4b07-98a7-c75d2fea1413\" style=\"color:#000000;\">이 종이 두께는 A4 용지 3장 정도로 좋은 품질에 견고한 만큼, 오래 써도 쉽게 구겨지지 않습니다. 게다가 사진을 펼쳤을 때 자연스럽게 넘어가고, 손에 닿는 느낌도 부드럽습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-0ec4607e-3cb7-42a0-942b-3fa3d9779672\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-34bcfc18-b81d-4704-a55e-e2fa7f7f025b\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-8588cde6-3393-4ac9-bc30-151aedce2897\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-6eb22808-08e8-4f71-af29-76ed7478b122\" style=\"color:#000000;\">이런 디테일은 미니포토프린터로는 따라가기 어렵습니다. 휴대성은 좋지만, 인쇄 질감과 고급스러움은 포토북을 따라가는 데 한계가 있는 것입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-582fba6c-cbf2-4e64-9fb5-3682f64735c3\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-d7e5cbcb-e818-4049-b72f-14a43cf9ab73\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4de911be-6cc8-40df-802b-e2621daa4ca8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223833173933/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fe6da384-d520-4e29-9fa9-abf3f41281c2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-350056de-a4fa-4965-a8c5-7257ac7a042c\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-345e2d7d-f496-40b9-82dd-67cc6c414740\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-d7c04a74-d296-42f3-9012-11fcadf1900b\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-5cbed69a-b36b-4685-929e-2eff3a34f972\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">다</span>음으로는 코팅 처리입니다. 사진에 유광이나 무광 코팅을 하면 색이 더 생생하게 표현되고, 손자국이나 오염도 잘 생기지 않습니다.</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-6d2b7aaa-5ac0-4fcb-8fcf-94fec5be3cdc\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-5043bf8b-2335-4183-96dc-f690730a7a05\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b>무엇보다도 </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-e9c89577-4751-4307-a573-69ba14ac82d5\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b>점보포토는 UV 유광 코팅 옵션을 무료</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-6764a93b-e3f9-4189-8811-77bf61f58ad2\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b>로 제공하고 있어서 저렴한 가격하게 선명하고 더 오래 깨끗하게 보관할 수 있습니다. </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-04d5da37-d070-42bc-a5d4-736431de7ef8\" style=\"color:#000000;\">코팅을 원하지 않는다면 무광 옵션도 선택할 수 있습니다. 유광은 밝고 화사한 느낌, 무광은 종이 질감이 느껴지는 차분한 분위기로 연출할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-3912649c-9c0a-4a82-aa55-112877cea2c4\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-382b9420-41cd-454c-a191-eae11d45d588\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a07fc78d-1a43-4913-b084-8fed1da442dd\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223833173933/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4b7c211a-fd97-4b0a-8747-6b149f6b45c4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-c7c3f4cc-ade4-4938-a4ac-fc49335d782f\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-5eca380c-2705-4511-a27b-457299669649\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-c885de26-90aa-42d1-b406-c41e3e90a24a\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-1982bb45-929f-4311-a027-54939fd6ad6d\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">편</span>​</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-35c28a8a-b388-4649-b542-55bd585642c8\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>집 기능을 제공하는 포토북 사이트인지도 확인해야 합니다. </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-7fc97bb6-b474-432b-bb94-d1b8c328353f\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b>점보포토 편집기</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-f3aae7c9-f0c6-40fc-bb45-3c2c9814755e\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b>는 누구나 쉽게 사용할 수 있게 구성돼 있습니다. 다양한 레이아웃, 배경, 아이콘, 말풍선 등으로 나만의 스타일로 꾸밀 수 있고, 프롤로그와 에필로그 페이지도 넣을 수 있어 이야기를 담기에도 좋습니다.</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-3c6df2f5-96fa-4e1d-968d-374163319ef9\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-40d1a698-c57c-4a90-82c6-8162bb7f675d\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-dd22bf80-d3c9-46a0-997d-69c963092391\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-5dfe69bf-1589-4997-aaec-7f2ad12abeac\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-506f4670-c732-4633-a075-17867b61e16c\" style=\"color:#000000;\">미니포토프린터로 뽑은 사진은 따로 정리해야 하지만, 포토북은 편집기 하나로 한 번에 정리하고 완성할 수 있습니다. 특히 편집 중에 사진 밝기나 색감을 보정할 수 있어, 원본보다 더 예쁘게 만들어질 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-8213b090-2664-44cb-95b4-5104fad3e1fe\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-8892c94f-617b-4302-b764-4e883743e5b0\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0e2b61af-b4af-44b8-a4eb-f4ab7078d57a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223833173933/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dbe09466-76dc-4722-a4c4-7f91aa9a9080\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-cbf3ab97-c79b-492f-98f1-c095a5089e76\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-b3519e2e-bc0c-45c3-bb76-14e7e717f726\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-700f4a8d-354b-473e-ba80-539b0d1b59b0\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-aa2f3aa3-73bb-413c-9c71-77e3b64fd70b\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">이</span>런 점들을 보면, 점보포토 포토북은 벚꽃 사진을 보관하고 꾸미기에도 정말 좋은 선택입니다. </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-527c54d0-beec-4edb-9169-a7fcf39a598c\" style=\"color:#000000;\">벚꽃 사진은 색감이 중요한 만큼 인쇄 품질을 확인하셔야 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-6256e614-1adf-494e-83e4-0e6bbd14a8cd\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-6af951ec-5de0-4040-bf79-813bb1872817\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-44445e79-2569-4814-b7f5-9799bde0f13f\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-0ac777f9-483c-40d2-a938-cdb477dd5b46\" style=\"color:#000000;\">이러한 색감 좋은 포토북 한 권에 스토리처럼 구성해서 정리하면 사진을 넘길 때마다 그날의 감정과 분위기가 다시 떠오릅니다. 미니포토프린터로는 만들기 힘든 디자인과 구성을 할 수 있는 겁니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-524b3eee-9a9a-48aa-9056-821e5541981d\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-537955dc-f487-4bc8-8829-09761520543b\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-283fa82b-ca24-453c-b173-269585792da9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223833173933/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a7f93459-9348-43f6-a503-c461f0a27462\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-96ad1720-a922-4937-9d3b-6cf835f44dc5\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-d10f9ab7-ea13-458b-ab87-078b01ec72d3\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-0d7e0115-f992-4961-873b-bd1bfdfd8dc0\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-fa81b1dc-ec84-4917-aaf6-98501e3cad9e\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">포</span>토북은 구성도 자유롭습니다.</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-b818e782-6250-4dd8-be34-147582bae58c\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> 다양한 페이지 배치와 분할 구성을 선택할 수 있어 사진이 많을 때도 정리하기 좋습니다. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-3a975c4d-47be-4337-9b6f-cf675e14076c\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b>점보포토 실제 이용자들도 “사진을 앨범으로 만들었더니 훨씬 보기 좋다.”, “사진 넘기면서 여행을 다시 떠올릴 수 있어서 감동했다”라는 후기를 주셨습니다.</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-b1d20d9d-9882-4ae9-ae17-67532dd5e174\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> 미니포토프린터를 쓰다가 포토북을 이용해 본 분들도 차이를 크게 느끼고 만족해하셨답니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-56aab7c1-40ca-4b0f-9adb-86e2046df070\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-c27262be-d2d5-46a6-b013-791329aeeee7\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c6e728aa-d490-49fa-99ec-8edfa342f97d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223833173933/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e13a09f9-84b8-45cc-b8c2-6152a52989b2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-9e2526b2-b6c8-4b96-b058-c29f57a8f4dd\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-efebe406-b77b-421b-91fc-eefb07b824f7\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-cbef2a62-9413-47d4-b0eb-e84a6e15d42a\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-26896e2e-779e-44a3-9a09-b9c6bf07a015\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">“</span>사진을 많이 찍는데 포토북으로 정리해 놓는 방법도 괜찮다.”, “포토북 한 권에 시간의 흐름이 정리된 느낌이라 자주 꺼내보게 된다”라는 후기도 많이 받고 있습니다.</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-55078a70-75f4-406b-a4d1-980aed2acdf3\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b> 미니포토프린터는 빠르게 출력할 수 있다는 점에서 좋지만, 특별한 추억을 제대로 담고 싶다면, 이번엔 포토북으로 만들어 보시길 바랍니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-d6fb9545-8711-40b2-8a10-af85fa870c02\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-0615e0cd-bdd0-464b-ab48-bd105392625a\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ccd78a51-ffb2-45a6-8491-60230c202fb7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223833173933/009.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2b7b9a16-765c-42ab-a0cc-cf1cd2f3d4e3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-64b487bf-9249-4df8-95a6-1916c73b55a5\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-4616808e-8b45-4cbd-a4eb-d7326b1ea142\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-d220342e-4fc8-42ef-ade1-1387b66e6ba6\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-e52e1f3b-58f4-48c4-9e4e-282e9da44614\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">제</span>​</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-5cdc5bb4-de35-4312-9298-eff69f5ce5f3\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>작 과정도 간단합니다.</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-820140f4-1f2a-4d34-a7df-41596e00a0bb\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-592d9b5b-851f-4e52-a7f8-8df222f3093a\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#b0f1ff;\">점보포토 웹사이트나 앱에서 포토북 상세페이지에 접속해 '만들기' 버튼을 클릭하면, 전용 편집 프로그램이 실행됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-9203f9bd-493f-4aa8-b320-f9db2fccdb6e\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d1a69a16-02eb-4434-893d-7c869c2d8b11\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-98798132-a611-4c98-a5ec-343389ec4f7a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223833173933/010.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-60b47d54-32db-462d-8be0-65a7f99fb63a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-d35b7694-9283-447b-a08d-4bfcd10e7af0\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-06fd781e-bb4e-4599-ac1d-7dc31b67c0b2\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-b17ea421-ddc7-4b7e-8140-a7afd8c6a7ed\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-5ec32c74-8a8b-434c-bc05-75bedb140384\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">이</span>곳에서 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-e30c556c-90f7-4744-aa92-7595b4780e52\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#b0f1ff;\"><b>포토북 디자인을 선택하고 사진을 추가하며, 배경, 문구, 아이콘, 말풍선 등 디자인 요소도 자유롭게 편집할 수 있습니다. 원하는 구성이 완성되면 '저장하기'를 누른 후 주문서로 이동해 결제를 완료하면 됩니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-cb3efe97-43b7-4bcb-b75d-93a7c4f62288\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-e4d4aff2-4daa-4a08-b755-9c7cae3cd9a3\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0f6ef5b3-bc63-4a98-a6cc-a0a78b556ac3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-re