p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-fc1fff61-0aeb-4d09-a407-9e7ed87e15d4\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-cebe7dfa-f543-40b8-923d-37b308a79971\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#b0f1ff;\"><b><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">이</span>후 점보포토에서는 ① 사진 출력 ② 표지 코팅 ③ 표지 제작 ④ 내지 코팅 ⑤ 성책(내지와 표지 합본) 공정이라는 제작 과정을 꼼꼼하게 거쳐 포토북을 완성합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-e38b1b32-56b7-457f-98b9-d3748b55b04d\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-4a8053b4-e9fd-47cc-b538-29c285b9a7cd\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-28ad1dc4-e840-47b4-b97f-87e9116ee865\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-0b9de105-deb4-4ae4-a22c-ba690ddda8ef\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">먼</span>저, </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-72a33fc7-2d0c-4bde-878a-28d1c079a700\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b>고객님이 편집한 내용을 바탕으로 고화질 사진 출력</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-f04110c4-e4ce-4072-9b75-f2ce6567121c\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>이 진행됩니다. 그다음 단계에서는</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-9f3ff055-8596-4f97-82f4-5e01202099f6\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b> 포토북 표지에 UV 유광 코팅을 입혀 색감을 더욱 생생하게 표현하고, 손자국이나 오염으로부터 보호할 수 있도록 마감 처리</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-1ed2f013-1ecb-4b22-9d1c-09d3aaa24ee4\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>가 이루어집니다. 이 UV 코팅은 무료로 제공되고 있고, 오랜 기간 깨끗한 상태로 보관하실 수 있답니다.</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-7931c5ca-2f7f-43dd-9980-9957ebbdffb9\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-98d60880-6a68-4451-a59a-839413938e0c\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-4b0f36ce-e0d0-481d-93f5-59b8a064bf41\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-video se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-video\" id=\"SE-8dfeba1d-ca62-4a3f-b805-11512e07b296\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-video se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-video\" id=\"SE-71227b51-5224-4a90-9063-9ca27efe8ea0\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-video se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-video\" id=\"SE-e386fac8-845d-461b-92df-a3b37993ee7a\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8e9335d7-500d-4fa9-bf96-c605ded94286\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-c207372b-db25-4e8b-8228-4511b8af8d14\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-1b99fb1f-2d9e-4cc0-99e3-1d68781df73b\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-93b5e2c6-404c-4f2d-a7b5-c1d1661537b1\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-e78ec68d-52b4-4727-b69c-c8054b580757\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">표</span>지는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-17f2c7d9-b6e6-47aa-9a75-2030e0be1c5a\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b>단단한 하드커버 재질로 제작</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-418be83c-e871-4b21-8dce-c2294b1b2084\" style=\"color:#000000;\">되고,</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-09aee3ac-1c75-42ca-a68e-837398ae53c6\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b> 내지 또한 유광 또는 무광 중 선택한 방식으로 코팅되어 고급스러운 질감과 높은 내구성을 제공합니다. </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-5c09af46-ab0f-4566-9a82-bbbcae7782a1\" style=\"color:#000000;\">이후에는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-6a3189cc-90cf-45d2-a643-e97baee2219f\" style=\"color:#00cdff;\"><b>완성된 표지와 내지를 하나로 합치는 '성책 공정'을 통해 견고하게 제본</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-57d9c316-fca7-4d13-a301-ccff9873cd1a\" style=\"color:#000000;\">됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-52fbffa9-43ae-4f56-b4d8-0cc0ace47e8b\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-3abc4794-4c30-4ff4-91dd-6a1d3d16a938\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-video se-section-align-justify se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-video\" id=\"SE-adf586b3-e5f9-4a84-8f0a-cb6b71487660\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-video se-section-align-justify se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-video\" id=\"SE-167facc3-9e07-4862-9e8e-a1f6fc3e4472\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-460f36a3-9c06-46e0-8636-88782ea12069\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-8386ac71-87d8-4db6-84e2-57d1ff9462ba\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-34f768c8-c368-4462-8d34-3be0a6778f68\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b> </b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-fd077c34-af7f-4672-bcf1-02168642c7cb\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-31d28cc9-8762-4f4f-be53-573032b38297\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">이</span> 모든 과정을 거치는 데에는 평균 1~2일이 소요되며, 제작이 완료된 포토북은 충격 방지 포장으로 꼼꼼하게 포장한 뒤 안전하게 고객님 댁으로 배송된답니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-1f3df67e-33c5-4514-b9d4-9ad0306cd6a5\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-fabe8b8f-df79-477e-9c87-66249b8ff9a5\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e84afc67-4bba-4fbd-834e-6c4391c284e8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223833173933/014.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-52904534-a293-49e3-8c26-e849d1b49180\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-17e8085e-c070-47bb-acbe-86625622ce93\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-d7e7f4e9-b418-4144-9525-5e0dc8a20450\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-95948c40-e9b6-4991-9e74-27fee71597a6\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-2652ed56-6864-4d3b-b556-dfe1d3094157\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">매</span>년 봄은 돌아오지만, 올해 벚꽃은 다시 오지 않습니다. 그래서 벚꽃 사진은 더 소중하게 남겨야 합니다. 미니포토프린터로는 부족한 부분을 포토북으로 채워보시면 어떨까요?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-91f670eb-b164-478c-b97c-820238dfe32b\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-06aff3b5-9cf8-4bbc-9810-e177ecaaf08a\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2c0b0a42-9a38-49bc-81bc-681aed4dc0df\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/jumbo_blog@5bcf03a7fa328fe2ff9dd7eb0e37da732a641b7d/223833173933/015.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-65d79d6a-fc88-43a2-a64a-abd2c5588ae8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-5909d96d-a582-4491-8e1a-2c45c8bb0ccc\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-45a0c837-5deb-4142-a704-e0fffaaa877e\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><span class=\"se-drop-cap\"> </span>​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify se-text-paragraph-drop-cap\" id=\"SE-a87ee8a4-ba99-4ea4-acf3-0e58ae770d44\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-45d71f46-ef34-48b3-8801-2fdc8bc9f3a1\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><span class=\"se-drop-cap\">포</span>토북은 오래 보관할 수 있고, 선물로도 좋고, 책장에 꽂아두면 매년 꺼내보게 되는 특별한 앨범이 됩니다. 실제로 많은 분이 여행, 가족 행사, 계절 사진 등 다양한 주제로 포토북을 만들고 만족하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-4f04d799-9c96-4837-9c76-a9f5e7d9f5f8\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-38b2207c-ed5a-451b-bee0-7e05441d6245\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-459b6af5-8333-4ea1-a67d-fa6357a80f83\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-e073b2ae-2fa4-42b0-9585-deb908cdd2eb\" style=\"color:#000000;\">벚꽃 사진을 어떻게 남길지 고민 중이라면, 미니포토프린터보다는 점보포토 포토북으로 완성도 높게 남겨보시길 바랍니다. 봄날의 감성이 그대로 담긴 포토북 한 권이 추억을 더 오래, 더 선명하게 간직해 줄 것입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-90a1c20c-0461-4186-aded-e56d342af9a0\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-98a5168e-3b21-4ad9-b530-e8f6f3819037\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-video se-section-align-justify se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-video\" id=\"SE-a6c6162c-3ccb-46db-bb66-bea79617799b\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0bc0d02f-6649-4216-9c45-8d1fa4096b04\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-7ce1e674-449d-48a7-90e7-d4a8ef583c1f\" style=\"line-height:1.9;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-b60aa537-d3ab-4aec-84ad-2efe51d5c219\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
